@Suppy.InventoryUpdate.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5253
@accessToken = paste_access_token_here
@batchId = paste_batch_id_here
@tenantId = tenant_1

### Liveness
GET {{Suppy.InventoryUpdate.Api_HostAddress}}/health/live
Accept: application/json

###

### Readiness
GET {{Suppy.InventoryUpdate.Api_HostAddress}}/health/ready
Accept: application/json

###

### Submit product batch update
POST {{Suppy.InventoryUpdate.Api_HostAddress}}/api/products/batch-update
Content-Type: application/json
Idempotency-Key: tenant-1-batch-001
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "tenantId": "{{tenantId}}",
  "items": [
    {
      "itemId": "123",
      "price": 100,
      "stock": 50,
      "metadata": {
        "source": "http-file"
      }
    }
  ]
}

###

### Check product batch status
GET {{Suppy.InventoryUpdate.Api_HostAddress}}/api/products/batches/{{batchId}}
Accept: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

###

### Retry failed product batch items
POST {{Suppy.InventoryUpdate.Api_HostAddress}}/api/products/batches/{{batchId}}/retry
Accept: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

###

### List products by tenant
GET {{Suppy.InventoryUpdate.Api_HostAddress}}/api/products?tenantId={{tenantId}}&page=1&pageSize=50
Accept: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

###
